sequenceDiagram
   participant UI as Browser UI
   participant API as FastAPI
   participant DB as SQLite
   participant PIPE as Pipeline

   UI->>API: POST /api/sessions
   UI->>API: POST /api/sessions/{id}/input
   UI->>API: POST /api/sessions/{id}/config
   UI->>API: GET /api/sessions/{id}/stream?mode=analyze
   API->>DB: status = running
   API->>PIPE: start worker thread
   PIPE-->>API: progress events
   API-->>UI: event: progress
   PIPE-->>API: result payload
   API-->>UI: event: result
   API-->>UI: event: done
